{"tid":1493021,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"特朗普稱貿易戰或短期對美國不利　惟必須對抗中國","createTime":"2019-08-21T05:34:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-21T05:41:18.000Z","uid":141151,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"897be532bafeb866d424b4fabeb967fe2888656a","tid":1493021,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T05:34:03.000Z","msg":"特朗普稱貿易戰或短期對美國不利　惟必須對抗中國<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1475825-20190821.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1475825-20190821.htm&d=0fhT0ZiErqSmjIt08Df9orHKdwoo7KeUephkEgg9e70%3D&h=94064cc4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1475825-20190821.htm&h=60bb300f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1475825-20190821.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n美國總統特朗普說，中國一直在貿易問題上欺騙美國，因此即使貿易戰對美國經濟，構成短期傷害，他都必須在貿易問題上，與中國對抗。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普在白宮會見羅馬尼亞總統約翰尼斯後表示，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>中國已經佔了美國25年便宜，甚至是更長時間，因此無論對國家有利，抑或短期內對國家不利，他都必須採取行動。</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n特朗普又回應外界對美國經濟衰退的憂慮，強調美國經濟表現不錯，現時距離經濟衰退，仍然很遠，如果聯儲局願意減息，美國經濟將會出現前所未見的爆發性增長。"},{"pid":"dcf1ccd08594017f920c019764bc3ec913efa653","tid":1493021,"uid":248098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T05:35:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n對抗 chinazi <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e428762dd34db61af4c8a6abe1dd2afd9c2d30f8","tid":1493021,"uid":281926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T05:41:18.000Z","msg":"各位巴打絲打，頂住呀！<br />\n路還很長，記住齊上齊落！<br />\n香港人可攻可守！智勇雙全！<br />\n記住<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>永不分化！不割蓆！不篤灰！</strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>I